snippet.title: Robocop Vs. The Terminator (Sega Genesis) - Level 1: Flight Terminal
snippet.description:
Robocop Vs. The Terminator for the Sega Genesis. This is the first level of the game. I still have the old original cartridge lying around somewhere. The gameplay, however, is recorded on an emulator. I used to play this game when I was about 3-5 years old. Brings back a lot of memories. 

I'll be uploading videos of all the levels including the REAL VERSION cheat which unlocks new enemies.

All credit goes to the makers of the game: Interplay Entertainment, Virgin Games
